English:
Check[c][ffffff][b] 'glow colours'[/b] [-][/c]of the Cores:


[c][ffffff][b]Green[/b] - Player Core[-][/c]
Your stuff, your buddies, your rivals.

[c][ffffff][b]Red[/b] - NPC Core. [-][/c]
Non-player faction. With this Core, a structure's blocks will be protected from manipulation.

[c][ffffff][b]Pink; Blue[/b] -  "Admin"[-][/c]
For story and special dungeons. Turns the whole structure Indestructible.  
[sup]( Note: 1 )[/sup]
Will be displayed on the Map as a chevron (= 'Double arrows' pointing up.)

[i]--- [/i]
[sup][c][c0c0c0][i](1) - You might still be able to [b]hurt [/b]such a structure.[/i][-][/c]

[c][ffffff][b]红色[/b] - NPC核心。[-][/c]
非玩家派系。有了这个核心，结构的方块将受到保护，免受操纵。

[sup]（注意：1）[/sup]
将在地图上显示为一个倒V形（= '双箭头' 指向上方。）

English:
[i][b][c][c0c0c0]Note: For trying out building, the game's 'Creative Mode' is highly useful.[-][/c][/b]
[c][c0c0c0]Select it in the Main Menu -> Start new game -> Creative mode.[-][/c][/i]

- The game uses a Large grid and a Small grid.
- Blocks of [b][c][ffffff]different grid sizes cannot mix.[-][/c][/b]
- Each block fills a whole 'cube volume'.[i] (Compare to e.g. Minecraft)[/i]

- Certain devices can only be placed on the right structure type 
[i](E.g. a Hover Vessel or a Base. - - [/i]
[i]Check the block's description by hovering over it with your mouse in the inventory.)[/i]
Chinese (simplified):
[i][b][c][c0c0c0]注意：尝试建造时，游戏的 '创意模式' 非常有用。[-][/c][/b]
[c][c0c0c0]在主菜单 -> 开始新游戏 -> 创意模式中选择它。[-][/c][/i]

- 游戏使用大网格和小网格。
- [b][c][ffffff]不同网格大小的方块不能混合。[-][/c][/b]
- 每个方块填充一个完整的'立方体体积'。[i] (比如 Minecraft)[/i]

- 某些设备只能放置在正确的结构类型上
[i](比如悬浮飞船或者基地。 - - [/i]
[i]通过将鼠标悬停在库存中的方块上查看它的描述。)[/i]

English:
[i][c][c0c0c0][-][/c][/i]
[i][c][c0c0c0]Note: Block handling is much easier in the game's [b]Creative Mode![/b][-][/c][/i]

During a Survival game: 
If a structure already has a [c][ffffff][b]Core[/b][-][/c], that one might protect it from modifying blocks.
Destroy enemy / NPC Cores, if needed.

[b][c][ffffff]To pick up intact blocks:  [-][/c][/b]
- Have your [b]own Core [/b]placed on the target structure
- Use a [b]Multitool in the "Retrieve Blocks"[/b] mode [i]( [c][00ff00][RMB] [-][/c]to select. )[/i]

[i]Note: Logistics [c][00ff00][ F4 ] [-][/c]will help you handle large blocks, as long as you are close to a structure with containers.[/i]

如果一个结构已经有了[c][ffffff][b]核心[/b][-][/c]，那么它可能会保护它不被修改方块。

English: Three ways to create structures in the game:
Chinese (simplified): 游戏中创建结构的三种方式：

English:
[c][ffffff]A- [-][/c][b][c][ffffff]Place a 'Starter Block' on the ground. [-][/c][/b]
Then build on that with your blocks.
[i](The Starter will already include a Core, setting your Ownership of the structure.)[/i]

[b][c][ffffff]B- Spawn a pre-made structures with the 'Factory' [-][/c][c][00ff00][ F2 ][-][/c][/b]
[i](E.g. by designing a structure in Creative Mode, and then spawning it in Survival.[/i]
[i]You can also subscribe to [b]Steam Workshop[/b] builds, and place them this way.)[/i]

[b][c][ffffff]C- Take over an existing structure. [-][/c][/b]
[i](You might need to find and destroy its Core first)[/i]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][ffffff]A- [-][/c][b][c][ffffff]在地上放置一个“起始方块”。[-][/c][/b]
然后使用你的方块在此基础上建造。
[i]（起始方块已经包括了一个核心，设定了你对结构的所有权。）[/i]

[b][c][ffffff]B- 使用“工厂”[-][/c][c][00ff00][ F2 ][-][/c][/b]生成预制结构。
[i]（例如：在创造模式中设计一个结构，然后在生存模式中生成它。
你也可以订阅[b]Steam Workshop[/b]的构建，并以这种方式放置它们。）[/i]

[b][c][ffffff]C- 接管一个现有的结构。[-][/c][/b]
[i]（你可能需要先找到并摧毁它的核心）[/i]

English:
[c][ffffff]Things you do might affect how other factions (NPC) will react to you.[-][/c]

You will get an indication at top left screen size, that displays if they approve or disprove of an action.
[i]E.g. entering their territory with a vessel, drilling ore deposits... or shooting at them.[/i]

[c][ffffff]'Unfriendly' and 'hostile' factions will attack you. [-][/c]
[i][b]Stealing [/b]from containers is _very much_ hated in the whole of the galaxy, so be careful![/i]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][ffffff]你的行为可能会影响其他派系（NPC）对你的态度。[-][/c]

你会在屏幕左上方看到一个指示器，显示他们是否批准或不批准你的行动。
[i]例如：进入他们的领地、钻取矿石资源...或者向他们开火。[/i]

[c][ffffff]“不友好”和“敌对”的派系会攻击你。[-][/c]
[i][b]在银河系中，[/b]从容器中[b]偷窃[/b]是非常被憎恨的，所以要小心！[/i]

English:
- [c][ffffff]Small Vessels [-][/c](SV) can warp inside of a star system.
- [c][ffffff]Capital Vessels[-][/c] (CV) can warp between stars.

You will need a 'Warpdrive' block and a 'Pentaxid tank' filled with fuel.
Select the target in the map (system or galaxy view). 
Then accelerate towards it, and press[c][00ff00] [K] [-][/c]to jump.

---

[i][c][c0c0c0]For training purposes, this [b]tutorial uses an exception[/b]- - Allowing you to warp to a different star, once, with a special SV.[-][/c][/i]
Chinese (simplified):
- [c][ffffff]小型飞船 [-][/c](SV) 可以在恒星系统内翘曲。
- [c][ffffff]主力舰[-][/c] (CV) 可以在恒星之间翘曲。

你需要一个'翘曲引擎'方块和一个装满燃料的'翘曲水晶（原料）'罐。
在地图中选择目标（系统视图或星系视图）。
然后加速向它前进，并按[c][00ff00] [K] [-][/c]进行跳跃。

---

[i][c][c0c0c0]出于训练目的，这个[b]教程使用了一个例外[/b]- - 允许你使用特殊的SV翘曲到不同的恒星，一次。[-][/c][/i]

English: Congratulations! You have completed the Tutorial. See you in the Maingame for your Galactic Adventure ! Thank you for playing!
Chinese (simplified): 恭喜！ 你已经完成了教程。 在主游戏中，期待你的银河冒险！ 感谢你的游玩！
